profile:
Canridge Construction Inc. is a premier contractor throughout Saskatchewan since 2008. We were founded on the principle of “Quality Premium Craftsmanship.” This principle has guided Canridge over the years in our entire service fulfillment. Our expert teams of skilled craftsmen provide the highest quality of workmanship for your interior & exterior remodeling projects. We offer high quality remodeling products and a 100% commitment to you, the customer!

Canridge Construction Inc. takes pride in each project that we complete. This pride is evident in the meticulous preparation, installation, and clean up of each job site. There is no project that is too insignificant not to command our full attention and high professional standard.
Canridge would like to thank all of our past, present, and future customers for their continued support. We realize that without our valued customers’ support this organization would cease to exist.

“Building mutually beneficial relationships, one customer at a time.”
products:

Kitchen Remodeling
Basement Remodeling

services: At Canridge Construction Inc. we offer a wide range of remodeling solutions. We do everything from totally remodeling your kitchen and bathroom to the exterior of your home. We can guide you through the remodeling process no matter how detailed-oriented or simple your project may be. Our level of involvement allows us to oversee each project in its entirety and ensure quality workmanship every step of the way.

profile:
COMPANY MISSION
Building mutually beneficial relationships one customer at a time.

Canridge Construction Group Inc has been serving the residents of Saskatchewan since 2008.  Canridge prides itself on professionalism, customer satisfaction and ensures that all services are provided to the highest standard. The founding principle that has guided Canridge over the years is “Quality Premium Craftsmanship”.  This is demonstrated through the pride, dedication, and attention to detail that goes into each job.
We strive to be Saskatchewan’s leader in the installation of premium quality roofing and exterior building systems.  Through the strength and expertise of our employees, Canridge has sustained its business success by providing innovative exterior building solutions to our clients.
In 2015 we were proud to be the recipient of the Better Business Bureau of Saskatchewan Torch Award for the Trades and Contractor category, along with receiving a certificate of achievement from Saskatchewan Workers Compensation Board.
We now offer financing through FinanceIt.
